quran[357]{c,v,t}:
  36,28,"Ntitwa bamanuriye abantu biwe arizo ngabo zivuye mw’ijuru, inyuma yiwe kandi ntitwari mubazi manura"
  36,29,"Ntacabaye atari akaruru kamwe nk’isase, bose baca bara zimangana"
  36,30,"Vyari\tkuba\tngombwa\tmukuba\thumuriza\tabo\tbantu\tbatashikiwe n’intumwa y’Imana n’imwe, mugabo bamye bijajurira gusa"
  36,31,Mbega ntibabona abantu isinzi twahoneje imbere yabo yuko batagaruka iwabo
  36,32,Kandi nta muntu uwariwe wese atazo shengezwa imbere yacu
  36,33,"N’ikimenyetso\tkiri\tkuribo\tn’Isi\tyapfuye,\ttuzoyizura\tnugukura\tmuriyo imbuto bazohora bafungura"
  36,34,"Tugira muriyo imirima hamwe n’ibiti vy’imitende n’imizabibu\thamwe nugu cishamwo amariba muriyo"
  36,35,"Kugira ngo bafungure muri ivyo vyamwa, kandi n’amaboko yabo ntaco yakoze, mbega ntibashima"
  36,36,Hahayagizwa Imana yaremye ikigabo n’ikigore muri vyose muvyo Isi inagisha no mumitima yabo hamwe nivyo batazi
  36,37,"N’ijoro\tn’ikimenyetso\tkuribo\tkuko\tariho\tbakura\tmwo\tumurango, mumwanya bagaca baba mumwijima"
  36,38,"N’izuba\trigenda\tgushika\tkugituro\tcaryo,\tiryo\tn’iteguro\try’uwufise ububasha n’ubumenyi"
  36,39,"N’ukwezi\ttwagupimiye\tibituro\tvyakwo\tkugeza\tnaho\tgusubira\tkuba gutoyi cane nk’igishishwa c’icamwa c’umutende gishaje cane"
  36,40,"Ntazuba rishikira\tUkwezi canke Ijoro ngo rirenge Umutaga, mugabo vyose biguma birerembera munzira zavyo"
  36,41,"N’ibimenyetso\tkuribo\tbimenyesha\tyuko\ttwajanye\tabavyeyi\tbabo mumato yari yuzuye mwo ibintu"
  36,42,Twabaremeye ivyo burira ko bimeze nkivyo bazo kurira ko
  36,43,Nitwa shaka twoshobora kuba somesha nturi kandi ntamufasha azoba arimwo canke uwuzoba rokora
  36,44,Atari kumpuhwe zivuye iwacu hamwe nukuba girira akamaro mukiringo kigufiya
  36,45,"Mugihe babwiwe bati:- nimutinye ibiri imbere yanyu hamwe n’ibiri inyuma yanyu kugira ngo muronke imihezagiro y’Imana"
  36,46,Ntakimenyetso icarico cose kibashikira mubimenyetso vy’Umuremyi wabo atari uko batavyitaho
  36,47,"Mugihe babwiwe bati:- nimutange muvyo Imana yabahaye, bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri baca babwira abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri bati:- mbega tubarishe ibifungurwa mubo Imana yishakiye wenyene mwebwe ntimurimwo atari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  36,48,"Nabo bavuga bati:- iri sango rizoba ryari nimwaba muvugisha ukuri"
  36,49,Ntaco barindira atari ijwi rimwe gusa rizo sokora imitima yabo mugihe bazoba bariko baratongana aba nabariya
  36,50,Kandi ntibazo shobora kuraga muri ico gihe canke ngo bashobore kugaruka ku bantu babo
  36,51,"Munyuma hazovuzwa inzamba, mukanya isase uzoca ubona bazutse bavuye muntatemwa zabo bagenda ningoga na ningoga bagenda ku Muremyi wabo"
  36,52,"Bavuga bati:- yo! mbega ni nde yatuzuye muntatemwa zacu, ibi nivyo twemerewe nayene imigisha nivyo bavuze vy’ukuri intumwa z’Imana"
  36,53,"Ntakizoba atari iborogo rimwe gusa, mukanya isase gusa bose bazoba bamaze gushengezwa imbere yacu"
  36,54,"Uwo musi rero umutima w’umwumwe wese ntuzohemukirwa n’ikintu nakimwe, kandi ntimuzo rihwa impembo iyariyo yose atari kuvyo mwahora mugira"
  36,55,Mu vy’ukuri abantu bo mw’ijuru kuri uno musi bari mubikorwa vyabo biba nezereza
  36,56,"Abo\tbantu\thamwe\tn’imiryango\tyabo\tbari\tmubitutu\tbegamiye kunyegamo z’iteka"
  36,57,"Bazoronkerayo ivyamwa, kandi baronkereyo ivyo bipfuza mwo vyose"
  36,58,"Amahoro\tgusa\tniryo\tjambo\trizoba\trivuye\tku\tMuremyi\twabo\tnyene imigisha"
  36,59,Uno musi nimwi tandukanye nabo bantu babi
  36,60,Mbega sinaba buriye mwebwe bantu yuko muto hirahira ngo musenge Shetani mu vy’ukuri n’umwansi wanyu ari k’umugaragaro
  36,61,Yuko mwonsenga jewe Mana yanyu kuko ariyo nziza igororotse
  36,62,Ntankeka Shetani yarazimije abantu benshi cane muri mwebwe mbega ico gihe nti mwiyumvira
  36,63,Rero uwu niwo wamuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu mwamye mwemererwa n’Imana yanyu y’ukuri
  36,64,Uno musi uri hejuru nimu winjire mwo kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu
  36,65,Kuri uwo musi tuzoziba iminwa yabo hanyuma amaboko yabo atuganirire ateko amaguru yabo abe ivyabona kuvyo bamye n’ivyemezo n’amaguru yabo abe kuvyo bahora bagira
  36,66,"Iyo dushaka twari kunogora amaso yabo bakaguma birukira mumayira, mugabo izo nzira bazibone gute"
  36,67,"Iyo dushaka twari kubagira ibikoko ubwo nyene naho bari, rero ntibari gushobora kugenda iyo baja canke gusubira inyuma iyo bavuye"
  36,68,"Nuwo duhaye ubuzima burebure tumusubiza inyuma mw’ishusho ryiwe ryambere, mbega ibi vyose ntibabishira mubwenge bwabo"
  36,69,"Natwe ntitwa mwigishije amajambo y’ubuhizi kandi ntivyoba kuriwe, kandi ntiyari kuba iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu atari uko ari icibutso n’igitabu kigaragaza ibikenewe vyose k’umugaragaro"
  36,70,Kugira ngo atuze uwuri muzima muribo kandi hemezwe ijambo kubatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  36,71,Mbega ntibabona yuko twebwe twabaremeye muvyo amaboko yacu yagize hamwe n’ibikoko batunze
  36,72,Nivyo bikoko twarabi gamburukije rero murivyo birurirwa n’ibindi navyo biraribwa
  36,73,"No muri ivyo bikoko barabironkera mwo akamaro kenshi hamwe n’ibinyobwa, mbega nikuki badashima"
  36,74,"Bagumanye\tizindi\tMana\taho\tkugumana\tImana\ty’ukuri\tkugira\tngo bafashwe nabo"
  36,75,Ntibashobora kubafasha nabo arizo ngabo zabo ziba cungereye
  36,76,"Rero ntibigutere agahinda kubera amajambo yabo, ntankeka twebwe dufise ubumenyi bw’ivyo banyegeza hamwe nivyo basemerera"
  36,77,"Mbega\tumuntu\tntazi\tyuko\ttwamuremye\tmw’Ima\try’intanga?\tnone yabaye mukeba wacu ari k’umugaragaro"
  36,78,"Yaradutangiyeko akarorero aribagira ukuremwa kwiwe aca avuga ati:- ni nde azozura amagufa y’abantu mugihe azoba yamaze kuvungagurika"
  36,79,"Vuga uti:- uwuzo yazura nurya yayaremye ubwambere, nawe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwukurema ibiremwa vyose"
  36,80,Niyo yabagiriye umukomezwa uvuye mugiti kibisi mukaba kuri ico giti namwe mucatsako
  36,81,"Mbega uwaremye Amajuru n’Isi mbega ntabushobozi afise bwukurema nk’aba yaremye, kubera iki nawe ari Umuremyi mukuru nyene ubumenyi bw’ibintu vyose"
  36,82,"Mu vy’ukuri itegeko ryiwe mugihe ishakiye ikintu icarico cose nukukibwira iti:- nube mumwanya isase kigaca kiba"
  36,83,"Aninahazwa ry’uwufise muminwe yiwe harimwo ubwami bw’ibintu vyose, niwe niho muzo subizwayo mwese"
  37,1,Ndarahiye kubatonze imirongo n’iyindi
  37,2,Kandi kuri barya batuza amabi yose
  37,3,Kandi kuri barya basoma ubutumwa bw’Imana
  37,4,Mu vy’ukuri Imana yanyu niyo yonyene gusa
  37,5,"Umuremyi\tw’Amajuru\tn’Isi\thamwe\tnibimwo\thagati\tyavyo\tkandi n’Umuremyi w’ubuseruko bwose"
  37,6,Ntankeka twebwe twarasharije Ijuru riri hafi kw’isharizo ry’Inyenyeri
  37,7,Nukuyi kingira n’amashetani yataye umurongo
  37,8,"Ntibashobore\tkwumviriza\tibiremwa\tvyeranda\tno\tmugihe\tbirukanywe kumpande zose"
  37,9,"Bazoshirwa kure, kandi bazoba bafise n’ibihano bitazoba vako"
  37,10,"Dukuye\tmwo\tuwusahuye\tikintu\tgitoyi\tmunyuma\tagaca\takurikiranwa n’igishirira gisayangana"
  37,11,"Nimubabaze muti:- mbega nibo bafise ishusho rikomeye cane canke barya twaremye, ntankeka ni twebwe twabaremye tubakuye mw’ivu rimatanye n’irindi"
  37,12,Mbega uratangara nabo babifata minenerwe
  37,13,Mugihe batujijwe ntiba gondozwa
  37,14,Mugihe babonye ibitangaro vyacu babifata minenerwe
  37,15,"Nukuvuga\tbati:-\tntivyari\tkuba\tibi\tvyose\tatari\tuko\tari\tuburozi\tburi k’umugaragaro"
  37,16,Mbega mugihe tuzosandaba nukuba ivu n’amagufa niko kuzoba ari ukuri kukuzurwa
  37,17,N’abatama bacu bakera
  37,18,"Vuga uti:- egome muri ico gihe muzoba muri mubihano bitazoba vako"
  37,19,Iyo mumuriro udahera hazoba hari induru yurutavana ko munyuma yaho bazobona umuhero w’Isi washitse
  37,20,"Bazovuga bati:- yo! Uwu niwo wamusi w’impembo"
  37,21,Uwu niwo musi wugucibwa urubanza mwahora muhakana
  37,22,Begeranye bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo hamwe n’abagenzi babo hamwe nabo bahora basenga
  37,23,"Aho\tgusenga\tImana\tnimuba\trongore\tmunzira\tyomu\tmuriro\tudahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  37,24,Nimuba hagarike mu vy’ukuri bazobazwa
  37,25,Mufise iki ko mutarokorana
  37,26,Kuri uwo musi bazoteterwa bimwe bitarabaho
  37,27,Bazokwinjira babazanya bamwe n’abandi
  37,28,"Bavuga\tbati:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tmwebwe\tmwamye\tmudushikira\tmunzira z’ukuri"
  37,29,"Nabo bishure bati:- ahubwo mwebwe bonyene ntimwari muba Isilamu"
  37,30,Ntabubasha twari dufise hejuru yanyu mugabo mwebwe nyene mwari mubataye umurongo w’ukuri
  37,31,Rero intahe y’Umuremyi wacu iramaze gucibwa ntankeka tuzoyihonja
  37,32,Nitwebwe bonyene twabatakaje tukaba twari mubantu bazimiye
  37,33,Rero mu vy’ukuri kuri uwo musi bazoba bari mubihano bakoranijwe hamwe
  37,34,Uku niko tuzogira abo bataye umurongo
  37,35,"Mugihe\tbahora\tbabwirwa\tyuko\tatayindi\tMana\titegerezwa\tgusengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atari Imana y’ukuri baguma banana"
  37,36,"Nukuvuga bati:- yo! twebwe dusige Imana zacu kubera uyo ategura amajambo y’ubuhizi nawe ari umusazi"
  37,37,"Ahubwo\tyaje\tafise\tukuri\tnukwemeza\tintumwa\tz’Imana\tzose\tzabaye imbere yiwe"
  37,38,Mu vy’ukuri mwebwe ntankeka muzohonja ibihano bibabaza cane
  37,39,Kandi ntimuzohembwa atari kuvyo mwahora mugira
  37,40,Dukuyemwo abantu beranda b’Imana bagize ibikorwa vyabo vyiza
  37,41,Abo bantu nibo bazoronka imigisha yabo bwite
  37,42,Ivyamwa vy’ubwoko bwose kandi baterwe n’iteka ntangere
  37,43,Mumirima y’imigisha myiza
  37,44,Bari hejuru y’ubusaswa barabana n’abandi amaso kuyandi
  37,45,Bakikuzwa n’ibirahuri birimwo ibinyobwa vyiza cane
  37,46,Vyera derere bifise n’akanovera kuri abo bantu babinywera mwo
  37,47,"Kuri\tivyo\tbinywobwa\tntangorane\tn’imwe\tzizoba\tzirimwo\tcanke ugutakaza ubwenge"
  37,48,Bazoba bari kumwe n’abapfasoni bafise amaso meza manini maniniya
  37,49,Abo bapfasoni bameze nk’amagi yabitswe neza
  37,50,Bazohura bamwe n’abandi babazanya
  37,51,"Hanyuma avuge umuvugizi umwe muribo ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nari mfise umugenzi"
  37,52,"Uwahora ambwira ati:- mbega wewe uri muri bamwe bemera\tImana yabo y’ukuri"
  37,53,"Yuko\tmugihe\ttwebwe\ttuzo\tsandaba\tnukuba\tivu\tn’amagufa\tmbega twebwe tuzorihwa"
  37,54,"Nawe azovuga ati:- mbega muzo mu runguruka"
  37,55,Nawe azo runguruka aze amubone ari hagati y’umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  37,56,"Hanyuma aze amubwire ati:- ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana wewe wari wegereje kunzimiza"
  37,57,"Iyo\titaba\timigisha\ty’Umuremyi\twanje\tntankeka\tnari\tkuba\tmubo shengezwa n’ibihano vyo mumuriro udahera"
  37,58,Mbega na twebwe turi mu bantu bazo subira kwitaba Umuremyi wacu
  37,59,"Atari\turupfu\trwacu\trwaho\thambere\tkandi\ttwebwe\tntituzo\tsubira guhanwa"
  37,60,Ntankeka iyi niyo ntsinzi niniya
  37,61,Rero akarorero nkaka niko bogira abo bogira
  37,62,"Mbega ikaze nkiri siryiza, canke kuronka igiti citiriwe Zaqqum"
  37,63,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twagize ico giti nk’igihano caba hemukiye imitima yabo
  37,64,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tico\tn’igiti\tkivuye\thagati\ty’umuriro\tudahera\twitiriwe Jahannamu"
  37,65,Ivyamwa vy’ico giti bimeze nk’imitwe y’amashetani
  37,66,Ntankeka bazofungura kuri ico giti no kurico buzuze inda zabo
  37,67,Hanyuma ntankeka bazo shikirwa kubera uburure bw’ico giti n’uruvange rw’amazi y’amarike
  37,68,Hanyuma mu vy’ukuri ingaruka yabo bantu yazoba ari ayo mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  37,69,Mu vy’ukuri basanze abavyeyi babo barazimiye
  37,70,Nabo nyene baca batwarwa nugukurikira ingendo zabo
  37,71,Kandi ntankeka abantu benshi bakera barazimiye imbere yabo
  37,72,Mu vy’ukuri twararungitse abagabisha kuri abo bantu
  37,73,Rero nurabe uko yabaye amaherezo yabo bantu batujijwe
  37,74,Atari abagamburutsi b’Imana bigiriye ibikorwa vyabo vyiza
  37,75,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tintumwa\ty’Imana\tNuhu\t(iii)\tyaraduteye\takamo, n’abamwitavye b’intungane tumeze gute twebwe"
  37,76,Twaramurokoye hamwe n’abantu biwe bari muvyago bihambaye
  37,77,Twarahezagiye umuryango wiwe ngo babe aribo baguma kw’Isi
  37,78,Duca tumusigira ku bantu baje munyuma yiwe
  37,79,Amahoro y’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) asasagare kw’Isi yose
  37,80,Mu vy’ukuri uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,81,Mu vy’ukuri yari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,82,Munyuma yaho niho twaca twibiza bamwe n’abandi
  37,83,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (III) yari mumurwi wiwe
  37,84,Yarayikoreye idini y’Umuremyi wiwe n’umutima mwiza cane
  37,85,"Yaramubwiye\tSe\twiwe\thamwe\tn’abantu\tbiwe\tati:-\tmbega\tmwebwe musenga iki"
  37,86,"Kuvyiyadukije gusa vy’amamana aho yobaye Imana y’ukuri, nizo Mana mwipfuza"
  37,87,None n’ibihe vyiyumviro vyanyu hejuru y’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  37,88,Hanyuma yaciye yitegereza mu kwitegereza kunyenyeri
  37,89,"Avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndarwaye"
  37,90,Nabo baramuretse gutyo baca bamuha ibitugu barigira
  37,91,"Nawe aca agenda mumpisho no ku Mana zabo azibwira ati:- mbega mufise iki ko muda fungura"
  37,92,Mubaye gute ko mutavuga
  37,93,Hanyuma arahindukira abakubita n’ukuboko kwiwe kw’iburyo
  37,94,Baca baza n’ingoga na ningoga
  37,95,"Aca ababwira ati:- oh! Mbega musenga muvyo mwibaziye kubwanyu n’amaboko yanyu"
  37,96,Mugihe Imana ariyo yabaremwye hamwe nivyo mugira vyose
  37,97,"Nabo\tbishura\tbati:-\tnimu\tmwubakire\tinyubakwa\thanyuma\tmu mujugunyire muri uwo mukomezwa"
  37,98,"Rero bashatse kumu girira amarorerwa, mugabo duca\ttuba girira kuba aribo badebukiwe"
  37,99,"Nayo intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) yababwiye iti:- jewe ndagiye ku Muremyi wanje niwe azondongora"
  37,100,"Ewe Muremyi wanje, numpe mu bantu bagira ineza"
  37,101,Niho twamuha inkuru nziza y’ikibondo gitekanye
  37,102,"Mugihe yashika kurugero rw’ukugenda nukugaruka ari kumwe nawe niho yamubwira ati:- ewe kibondo canje, mu vy’ukuri jewe nabonye mundoto zanje yuko no kubaga, rero nawe niwiyumvire neza, none wewe ubibona gute? Nawe amwishura ati:- ewe data wanje nugire nk’uko wategetswe nanje uzonsanga Imana ibishatse ndimu bantu batenyenya"
  37,103,Bose hamwe uko ari babiri mugihe biyemeza imbere y’Imana nuguca amuryamika hasi kugira ngo amubage
  37,104,"Muri uwo mwanya isase twaciye tumu hamagara duti:- ewe ntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)"
  37,105,"Uramaze kwemeza yandoto yawe, mu vy’ukuri uku rero niko duhemba abagira neza bose"
  37,106,Ntankeka iri n’igeragezo riri k’umugaragaro
  37,107,Rero duca dukabisha n’igikoko cukubarwa gifise iteka ntangere
  37,108,Duca tumusigira kubaje munyuma yiwe
  37,109,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  37,110,Uku niko duhemba abantu bagira ineza bose
  37,111,Ntankeka yari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,112,"Hanyuma\ttwamuciriye\tagace\tyuko\tazokwibaruka\tintumwa\ty’Imana Is’haqa (iii) n’intumwa muntumwa z’ abagira ineza"
  37,113,"Duca turamu hezagira hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Is’haqa (iii) hamwe no muruvyaro rwabo, kuko aribo babaye mubagira ineza. hamwe n’abahemukiye imitima yabo bimwe bigaragara"
  37,114,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarabagiriye impuhwe intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Haruna (iii)
  37,115,Duca turaba rokora hamwe n’abantu babo mugihe bari mungorane zidasanzwe
  37,116,Duca tubakingira nabo baca baba bene intsinzi nyakuri
  37,117,Bose uko ari babiri twabahaye igitabu gitanga umuco
  37,118,Duca turabarongora munzira igororotse
  37,119,Hanyuma duca tubasigira mubaje munyuma yabo
  37,120,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe na Haruna (iii)
  37,121,Ntankeka uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,122,Ntankeka bari mubantu bacu bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  37,123,"Mu vy’ukuri, intumwa y’Imana Il’yaasiiyn (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana"
  37,124,"Mugihe yabwira abantu biwe ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya"
  37,125,"Mutabaza isanamu ryitwa Baa’la, mukareka gusaba umwiza wabaremyi"
  37,126,"Imana\tariyo\tmuremyi\twanyu\tn’Umuremyi\tw’abavyeyi\tbanyu\tbaho hambere"
  37,127,Baramu hakanye ntankeka rero bazo shengezwa mubihano
  37,128,Dukuyemwo abantu b’Imana basukuwe nayo nyene
  37,129,Twamusigiye kubaje munyuma yiwe
  37,130,Amahoro y’Imana abe kuntumwa y’Imana Il’yaasiiyn (iii)
  37,131,Ntankeka uku niko duhemba abagira ineza
  37,132,Mu vy’ukuri yari mubantu bacu bemera Imana yabo bimwe vy’ukuri
  37,133,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana
  37,134,Mugihe twamurokora hamwe n’abantu biwe bose
  37,135,Dukuye mwo umukenyezi ashaje mubasigaye inyuma
  37,136,Hanyuma niho twahonya abandi
  37,137,Mu vy’ukuri mwama mubacako mugitondo
  37,138,"No mw’ijoro nyene, mbega mwebwe ntimutegera"
  37,139,Mu vy’ukuri intumwa y’Imana Yunusu (iii) yari muntumwa z’Imana
  37,140,Mugihe yirukira mubwato bwikoreye ibintu vyinshi
  37,141,Baca bagira amatora aca aba mubatsinzwe nuguca atabwa mumazi
  37,142,Mukanya ifi ica iramumira mugihe yari muba taweko umwikomo
  37,143,Iyo ataba yari mubantu basenga Imana yiwe y’ukuri
  37,144,"Ntankeka\tyari\tkuguma\tmunda\ty’iyofi\tkugeza\tk’umusi\twizurwa ry’abantu bose"
  37,145,"Mugabo\ttwaciye\ttumujugunya\tkunkengera\tz’ikiyaga\tnawe\taremvye cane"
  37,146,Duca tumu nagishiriza uruyuzi rw’itango yaguma afungura
  37,147,Twaramutwaye ku bantu ibihumbi ijana n’abarenga
  37,148,"Baca baremera, nukuba nezereza kugeza kugihe caho basandabira"
  37,149,"Nimu\tbabaze\tmuti:-\tmbega\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tafise\tibibondo vy’abigeme nabo bakaba bafise ibibomdo vy’abahungu"
  37,150,"Mbega\ttwebwe\ttwaremye\tAbamarayika\tkuba\tyuko\taribo\tbakenyezi nabo bakaba ivyabona"
  37,151,Muragabe ku vyiyadukiza kuribo n’ivyo bavuga
  37,152,"Imana yaravyaye, mu vy’ukuri kuribo ntankeka n’ababeshi"
  37,153,Yoba yaratoye ibibondo vy’abigeme gusumba ibibondo vy’abahungu
  37,154,Mubayeho gute! Muca urubanza gute
  37,155,Yo! Mbega mwebwe aho muri ntimwibuka
  37,156,Canke mwebwe murafise ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro
  37,157,Nimuzane igitabu canyu ni mwaba muvugisha ukuri
  37,158,"Nabo bashizeho imiryango hagati yabo n’ibisigo, n’ivyo bisigo vyari vyamaze kumenya yuko atankeka kuribo bazo shengezwa"
  37,159,Imana iri kure n’ingene bayihayagiza
  37,160,Dukuye mwo abantu beranda batowe n’Imana
  37,161,Rero ntankeka mwebwe hamwe nabo musenga
  37,162,Ntimushobora kuba zimiza
  37,163,Atari bamwe bazo kwinjira mu muriro udahera
  37,164,Ntan’umwe muri twebwe atari uko afise ubwicaro bwiwe buzwi
  37,165,Mu vy’ukuri muri twebwe harimwo abatonda ku mirongo
  37,166,Hariho n’abandi muri twebwe bahayagiza Imana y’ukuri
  37,167,Mu vy’ukuri bamye bavuga
  37,168,Iyo tuba dufise igitabu nkuko babifise ba bantu baho hambere
  37,169,Ntankeka twari kuba mu bantu beranda b’Imana bisukuye
  37,170,Ico gitabu baragi hakanye rero ubu vuba bazomenya
  37,171,Kandi ntankeka ijambo ryacu riramaze gushika ku bantu bacu bahawe ubutumwa
  37,172,Yuko aribo bazo rokorwa
  37,173,N’ingabo zacu nizo zizo tsinda
  37,174,Rero nimu bareke kure mu mwanya mutoyi gusa
  37,175,Kandi mu bitegereze gusa nabo ubu vuba bazobona
  37,176,Yoh! barahimiriza ibihano vyacu
  37,177,Rero mugihe bizo manuka kurubuga rwabo hazoba hari mugitondo kitari ciza ku bantu batujijwe
  37,178,Nimu bareke mumwanya mutoyi gusa
  37,179,"Nurabe gusa, nabone ubu vuba bazobona"
  37,180,"Umuremyi\twawe\tari\tkure\tnivyo,\tUmuremyi\tw’iteka\thamwe\tn’ivyo bayihayagiza ko"
  37,181,N’amahoro y’Imana asasagare kuntumwa z’Imana zose
  37,182,"Nihayagizwa ryose ryiza niry’Imana, Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  38,1,"Swaad, (Insiguro y’iyi ndome hamwe n’uwufise ubumenyi bwayo bwose buzi Imana yonyene gusa). Ndarahiye kuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu ifise ubutumwa nyakuri"
  38,2,Mugabo abahakanye Umuremyi wabo bari mu bishima nugu higanwa
  38,3,"Twahoneje abantu bangahe imbere yabo, batako bakoma induru mugabo umwanya w’ukurokoka wamaze guhera"
  38,4,"Baratangaye mugihe bashikirwa n’uwutuza ava muribo hanyuma abatemera Imana yabo y’ukuri bavuze bati:- uyo muntu n’umurozi kandi n’umubeshi"
  38,5,"Yagize Imana zose kuba ari Imana imwe gusa, ntankeka iri n’ijambo ry’igitangaza"
  38,6,"Baciye bitahira bamwe mubakuru babo bavuga bati:- nimwigire kandi mwigumanire n’izo Mana zanyu, mu vy’ukuri iri n’ijambo rikenewe"
  38,7,"Twebwe ntitwigeze twumva ibi bintu yuko muri iyi migenzo yacu yanyuma, kandi ntivyamye ho ibi vyose atari uko ari ivyadutse gusa"
  38,8,"Niwe wenyene yamanuriwe ubu butumire gusa natwe ntitwabuhabwa, mugabo abo bantu bari bafise amakenga gusa kubera ubutumire bwanje, ahubwo ntibara honja ibihano vyanje"
  38,9,"Mbega barafise ububiko bw’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, nyene ubushobozi atanga vyose"
  38,10,"Canke barafise ubwami bw’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo, rero nibafate inzira ibashikana yo"
  38,11,Izi n’ingabo zizo gendeshwa ningoga muvyondo vy’abahakanyi vyagendeshejwe ningoga aho hambere
  38,12,Abaho hambere barahakanye abantu bo kuntumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) nabo kuntumwa y’Imana Aadi (iii) na Fir’auni nyene amazu y’inkingi zikoma komeye
  38,13,Na Thamuda hamwe n’abantu bokwa Lutwi n’abantu bo mukibira c’ibiti vyinshi iyo niyo mirwi yabo
  38,14,"Abo bose bara hakanye intumwa z’Imana, rero ibihano vyanje vyaraba shikiye"
  38,15,N’aba ntibarindira atari akaruru kamwe gusa kukuzurwa kwabo kata rindiriza
  38,16,"Bama bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, nutuzanire bimwe mubihano vyacu imbere yuwo musi wugu harurwa"
  38,17,"Nutenyenye kuri ivyo bavuga, mugabo wibuke wa muntu wacu mweranda ariwe Daudi (iii) nyene inguvu, mu vy’ukuri yari umuntu agaruka ku Mana n’ubu gamburutsi"
  38,18,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twara gamburukiye imisozi hamwe nawe ininahaze kuva k’umugoroba no mugitondo
  38,19,Hamwe n’inyoni zegereranijwe hamwe n’izindi zose zara mugamburukira
  38,20,Duca dushira mubwami bwiwe ubushobozi nukumuha ubumenyi bw’ugucira imanza abantu
  38,21,Mbega warashikiwe n’inkuru z’abari mumatati baca basimbira mucumba c’intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii)
  38,22,"Mugihe binjira kwa Daudi (iii) yarabatinye nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntutinye kuri twebwe turi mumatati, umwe muri twebwe yarahemukiye mugenzi wiwe, none nuducire urubanza rw’ukuri, kandi ntuhengame ahanaka kandi uturongore munzira igororotse"
  38,23,"Mu vy’ukuri uyu ni mwene wanje, afise intama z’inyana mirongo icenda n’icenda, nanje nkaba mfise inyana imwe gusa mugabo yavuze ati ndamuhe iyi rwanje ayitungire, none yananiye mu majambo"
  38,24,"Avuga ati:- ni vy’ukuri yaguhemukiye mukugusaba iyo ntungwa yawe mukwongereza kuntungwa ziwe, ntankeka abari mw’ishirahamwe benshi bama bahemukirana bamwe kubandi dukuyemwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza, nabo bantu bari kurushi, mu mwanya intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) yabona yuko twamuhaye ikibazo, aca asaba ikigongwe ku Muremyi wiwe n’ugupfukama n’ubwitonzi ntangere nugu tumbera ku Muremyi wiwe"
  38,25,"Duca tumugirira ikigongwe kuri ivyo vyose, mu vy’ukuri arafise kuri twebwe icubahiro kininiya n’ahantu heza"
  38,26,"Ewe Daudi (iii) mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaguhaye ubutegetsi ng’aha kw’Isi, rero nubacire abo bantu urubanza rw’ukuri kandi ntukurikire ivyo umutima wawe ushatse ntuze ukuzimize munzira nziza y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri bamwe bazimira nuguta inzira y’Imana abo bantu bazoronka ibihano bikaze cane kubera ukwibagira kwabo wa musi wuguharurwa"
  38,27,"Kandi twebwe ntitwaremye Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose kubusa gusa, ibi vyose nivyo bikeka bamwe batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri, rero ibihano bikaze cane vy’umuriro udahera bizoba shikira bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  38,28,"Mbega tubagire bamwe bemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza yuko boba bangana n’abononyi bagira ubwo bwononyi ng’aha kw’Isi, canke tubagire aba gamburukira Imana ko bangana n’abononyi"
  38,29,"Iki gitabu twakimanuye kuri wewe, kikaba gifise imihezagiro myinshi cane kugira ngo abantu bategere neza, iyumvire amajambo yaco hamwe n’abafise ubwenge nabo bategere neza"
  38,30,"Twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Daudi (iii) ikibondo citwa Suleymanu (iii) akaba yari mu bantu beza, kandi akaba yari afise n’ubwitonzi ntangere"
  38,31,Mugihe bwagoroba yashikirijwe Ifarasi zihumuye zihagaze nazo zikaba zari zihwahutse mugihe zitegetswe kwiruka
  38,32,"Yaciye avuga ati:- jewe nkunda ibintu vyiza mukwibuka Umuremyi wanje, mu nyuma zafarasi zinyegeza inyuma y’uruzitiro"
  38,33,"Nimu bagarure iwanje, hanyuma aca atangura kuzi hanagura kumaguru yazo no kumazosi yazo"
  38,34,Twaramuhaye intumwa y’Imana Suleymanu (iii) duca dushiraho uwundi mubiri hejuru y’inyegamo yiwe hanyuma aragaruka wenyene
  38,35,"Aca avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, nungirire ikigongwe kandi umpe n’ubwami, kandi ntuze ubuhe uwariwe wese munyuma zanje, ntankeka ni wewe mutanzi wa vyose"
  38,36,"Duca tumu gamburukiza umuyaga ugenda buhoro buhoro kw’itegeko ryiwe, naho ushaka gushika hose"
  38,37,Hamwe n’ibisigo n’abubatsi n’abibira mumazi
  38,38,N’ibindi bisigo biboshwe n’iminyororo
  38,39,"Iyi n’ingabirano yacu twaguhaye tutarinze guharurirana, rero nuyitange canke uyigumye utarinze kugiriranira ibiharuro"
  38,40,Mu vy’ukuri arafise kuri twebwe icubahiro n’ahantu heza
  38,41,"Kandi mwibuke intumwa yacu y’Imana Ayyubu (iii) mugihe Umuremyi wiwe yamuhamagara avuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri Shetani yanshikirije ibishoboka hamwe n’ingorane"
  38,42,"Ihute nuku kuguru kwawe, naya niyo mazi apfuse yukwisukira hamwe n’ayandi yukunywa"
  38,43,Duca tumuha abantu biwe hamwe n’abandi nkabo hamwe nabo kumigisha ivuye iwacu hamwe n’ubutumwa ku bantu bafise ubwenge
  38,44,"Nufate amasonga y’uduti mukuboko kwawe, hunyuma uce umukubitisha umucance wawe, kandi ntute indahiro yawe, ntankeka twebwe twamusanze ari mu bantu batekereje kandi n’intore, mu vy’ukuri yari muba gamburutsi bacane"
  38,45,Bibuke abantu bacu ariyo ntumwa yacu y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) na Is’haqa n’intumwa y’Imana na Yaaqubu bari bafise ubushobozi n’ubwenge buhagije
  38,46,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twagutoye kuri ryajambo ryiza cane ryukwibuka umusi w’imperuka
  38,47,"Kandi ntankeka abamyeho imbere yacu, nabo nimu bantu beza batowe"
  38,48,Kandi mwibuke intumwa y’Imana Ismaaili (iii) hamwe n’intumwa y’Imana Al’yasaa (iii) n’intumwa y’Imana Dhul’qiflu (iii) n’abo bose bari mu bantu b’intungane
  38,49,Ubu n’ubwibutso mu vy’ukuri abatinya Imana yabo y’ukuri igituro cabo caho bazo garukira hazoba heza cane
  38,50,Imirima yukwicara mwo mubuzima bwabo bwose izoba yuguruye imiryango yayo kubera bo gusa
  38,51,Bazo kwegamira kunyegamo basaba ivyamwa vyinshi hamwe n’ibinyobwa
  38,52,Hamwe nabo bazoba ho n’abanega babo bahumurije amaso yabo kubatambukanyi babo
  38,53,Ibi nivyo mwaraganiwe k’umusi w’imperuka
  38,54,Mu vy’ukuri iyi niyo migisha yacu idahera
  38,55,Nuko rero mu vy’ukuri bamwe barenga imbibe ingaruka zabo zizoba ziri ahantu habi cane
  38,56,Wamuriro witiriwe Jahannamu niwo bazokwinjiramwo naho nahateguwe nabi cane
  38,57,N’uku bizoba rero nibahonje amazi y’amarike n’amashira
  38,58,N’ibindi bihano nk’ibi ni vyinshi
  38,59,"Izi nizo ngabo zizo kwinjira hamwe namwe, mugabo ntizaronse ahantu heza zishikira mugabo zizo kwinjira mu muriro udahera"
  38,60,"Bavuze bati:- mwebwe ntakaze ryiza mufise mwebwe nimwe mwatumye turonka ibihano aho naho n’ahantu h’ubwicaro bubi cane"
  38,61,"Bavuze bati:- Muremyi wacu, abatumye tugira ibi vyose, n’ubongereze ibihano vy’incuro zibiri iyo mu muriro udahera"
  38,62,"Bazovuga\tbati:-\tvyabaye\tgute\tko\ttutababona\tbabantu\ttwahora tubaharura ko bari mu bantu babi"
  38,63,Erega twaraba kengereye mugabo amaso yacu ntiyababona gusa
  38,64,Ntankeka ibi bintu vy’amatati y’abantu bo mumuriro udahera nay’ukuri
  38,65,"Vuga\tuti:-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tjewe\tnd’uwutuza\tgusa,\tkandi\tntayindi\tMana itegerezwa gusengwa atariyo yonyene rudende nyene ubushobozi"
  38,66,Umumenyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nibirimwo vyose nyene ubushobozi hamwe n’ikigongwe cinshi
  38,67,"Vuga uti:- izi n’inkuru zihambaye cane"
  38,68,Mutitayeho namba
  38,69,Ntabumenyi nari mfise bw’ibiremwa bitagatifu mugihe batumvikana
  38,70,Simbwirwa ikintu na kimwe kuri jewe atari uko nd’umuntu atuza abantu kandi mboneka
  38,71,"Umuremyi wawe mugihe yababwira Abamarayika ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzorema umuntu ndamukuye mw’ivu"
  38,72,"Ninarangiza kurema uyo muntu nukumu huhera umutima uvuye\tkuri jewe, rero nimuce mumupfukamira nukumu gamburukira"
  38,73,Bara gamburutse Abamarayika bose uko bangana bose
  38,74,Dukuyemwo uwitwa Ibilisi yishimye nukuba muba hakanyi b’Imana
  38,75,"Imana yamubwiye iti:- ewe Ibilisi, n’igiki cakubujje ku gamburukira uwo naremye ku maboko yanje, mbega winamuye canke wabaye mubantu bakuru"
  38,76,"Nawe yishura ati:- jewe ndimwiza gusumba uyo waremye, kuko jewe wandemye unkuye mu muriro udahera, nawe umurema umukuye mw’ivu"
  38,77,"Imana\tica\tivuga\titi:-\tnuve\tmuri\tuwo\tmuriro\tudahera\tkuko\turamaze gutabwa kure n’imigisha yanje"
  38,78,Mu vy’ukuri umuvumo wanje uzoba hejuru yawe kuri kugeza k’umusi w’imperuka
  38,79,"Nawe yishura ati:- Muremyi wanje, numpe umwanya na mutoyi gusa kugeza k’umusi bazozurwa ibiremwa vyose"
  38,80,"Imana imubwira iti:- nivyo wewe uri mubaronse ikibanza c’ukubaho"
  38,81,Kugeza kumwanya w’umusi wategekanijwe
  38,82,"Nawe yishura ati:- ndarahiye k’ukuri kw’iteka ryawe ntankeka jewe abo bantu bawe nzobazimiza uko bangana bose"
  38,83,Dukuye mwo ba bantu bawe muribo ar’intore
  38,84,"Imana ivuga iti:- ndarahiye mvugishije ukuri"
  38,85,Mu vy’ukuri jewe nzokwuzuza mu muriro udahera kuri wewe Shetani hamwe n’abagu kurikira muribo
  38,86,"Vuga uti:- jewe sindaba saba impembo kuri ibi, kandi jewe sindi mu bantu bitegeka"
  38,87,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari ubutumwa ku bantu bose
  38,88,Kandi ntankeka mwebwe muzomenya inkuru ziwe mumwanya
  39,1,Imanuka ry’iki gitabu gitagatifu nikivuye ku Mana nyene ubushobozi hamwe n’ubuhizi buhagije
  39,2,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twaku manuriye iki gitabu bimwe vy’ukuri, rero n’usenge Imana yawe nukuyigira yuko ariyo Muremyi wenyene gusa"
  39,3,"Uwizerwa w’Umuremyi n’Imana yonyene gusa, mugabo bamwe bagira abandi kuba arizo Mana aho kuba ariyo yonyene rudende bavuga bati:- twebwe abo ntituba senga mugabo niba dushikane hafi cane y’Imana, mu vy’ukuri Imana izocira urubanza ruri hagati yabo kuvyo batumvikanye ko, ntankeka Imana ntirongora umubeshi w’umuhakanyi w’Imana"
  39,4,"Iyo Imana ibishaka ngo ironke ikibondo ntankeka yari gutora uwo yishakiye mubo yiremeye, mugabo iri kure yivyo vyose kuko n’Imana imwe yonyene rudende igira ivyo yishakiye"
  39,5,"Niyo yaremye Amajuru n’Isi bimwe vy’ukuri, ikaba ariyo yapfuse Ijoro hejuru y’Umutaga kandi ikaba ariyo yapfuse Umutaga hejuru y’Ijoro kandi ikaba ariyo yagamburukije Izuba n’Ukwezi vyose bikagira gusa kugihe categekanijwe, mumenye yuko ariyo nyene ubushobozi kandi ariyo nyene ikigongwe cinshi"
  39,6,"Niyo yabaremye mu mutima umwe, hanyuma igira mugenziwe kuba nkawe nukuba manurira ibikoko umunani harimwo impfizi n’inyana, rero ibarema munda z’abavyeyi banyu mufise iremwa ritandukanye n’irindi, riri mumyijima itatu, iyo rero niyo Mana ariyo Muremyi wanyu, ubwami bwose ni rwiwe kandi ntawundi asengwa bimwe vy’ukuri atariyo yonyene gusa, none mwebwe muhindukizwa hehe"
  39,7,"Ni mwaba muri ahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri, Imana ntibakeneye mwebwe mugabo ntiyemera ubuhakanyi bw’abantu bayo beranda, rero nimwa shima ivyo nivyo biyinezereza kuko biba bivuye kuri mwebwe, n’uwikorera ntazo kwikorera itu ry’uwundi, hanyuma ingaruka yanyu niku Muremyi wanyu, niyo izoba bwira ivyo mwahora mugira, ntankeka niyo ifise ubumenyi bw’ibiri mubikiriza vyanyu"
  39,8,"Mugihe umuntu ashikiwe n’ingorane yama atakambira Umuremyi wiwe nugu tumbera iwe, hanyuma imuhaye imigisha ivuye kuriyo, wa muntu aca yibagira kuvyo yahora imu hamagarira aho hambere hahise nukuyi gereranya n’ibindi bintu kugira ngo ibatakaze munzira yayo, wewe rero nuvuge uti:- nunezerwe kubera ubuhakanyi bwawe mukiringo gitoyi gusa kuko wewe uzoba uri mu bantu bo mumuriro udahera"
  39,9,"Mbega agire amasengesho mumyanya y’ijoro nugupfukama hamwe nuguhagarara nugutinya uwo musi w’imperuka hamwe nukwizera imigisha y’Umuremyi wiwe, wewe vuga uti:- mbega boshobora kungana bamwe bafise ubumenyi nabamwe badafise ubumenyi, rero abikebura nibarya bafise ubwenge gusa"
  39,10,"Vuga uti:- mwebwe bantu banje bemeye Imana y’ukuri, ni mutinye Umuremyi wanyu, bamwe bagira ineza iyariyo yose ng’aha kw’isi bazoronswa ivyiza\tvyabo,\tn’Isi\ty’Imana\tiragutse\tcane,\tkandi\tntankeka\tabatenyenya bazoronswa impembo yabo batarinze kurimburirana n’Imana"
  39,11,"Vuga uti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nategetswe yuko nsenga Imana nukwizera yuko Umuremyi ariwe wenyene gusa"
  39,12,Kandi nategetswe ngombe ndimu bantu bambere biyemeje kuba ndi umu Isilamu
  39,13,"Vuga uti:- jewe ntinya ibihano vy’umusi mukuru mugihe no cumurira Umuremyi wanje"
  39,14,"Vuga uti:- jewe nsenga Imana yanje nemeza yuko ariyo yonyene gusa kandi ariyo Mana"
  39,15,"Rero mwebwe nimusenge muvyo mukunda bitari Imana, nawe nuvuge iti:- mu vy’ukuri abazo ronka uruhombo nibarya bataye imitima yabo muruhombo hamwe n’abantu babo k’umusi w’imperuka, ni murabe urwo nirwo ruhombo ruri k’umugaragaro"
  39,16,"Hazoshirwa hejuru yabo ibicu vy’umuriro no munsi yabo hazobayo ibindi bicu, kuri ivyo rero Imana irabagabisha abantu bayo, namwe bantu banje nimutinye"
  39,17,"Na bamwe batitaho mukugira amasengesho y’amasanamu nuku gamburukira Imana, inkuru nziza nirwabo rero nubahe inkuru nziza aba bantu banje"
  39,18,"Nabumviriza amajambo bagakurikira ayafise akamaro kuribo abo bantu nibo Imana yarongoye, kandi nibo bafise ubwenge"
  39,19,"Mbega uwategerejwe gucirirwa urubanza rw’ibihano, mbega woshobora kurokora uwuri mumuriro udahera"
  39,20,"Mugabo aba gamburukiye Umuremyi wabo bazoronka amazu maremare agerekeranye kuyandi mazu maremare, munsi yayo mazu hazocamwo inzuzi, iyo niyo ndagano y’Imana, kuko Imana ntirenga kundagano yayo"
  39,21,"Mbega ntubona yuko Imana yamanuye amazi iyakuye mubicu hanyuma iyacisha hasi, nukuba amasoko y’amazi ari mukuzimu, hanyuma inagisha ivyamwa vy’ubwoko butandukanye, rero uca ubona ivyo vyamwa vyumutse nuguhindura amabara y’umuhondo, hanyuma bigaca bitangura gucika gurika, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ivyibutso ku bantu bafise ubwenge"
  39,22,"Mbega umuntu Imana yugururiye igikiriza ciwe nukwemera ubu Isilamu kandi akaba ari mumuco uvuye ku Muremyi wiwe, rero ibihano bikaze cane bizoshikira bamwe bafise imitima y’agatimatare batibuka Imana namba, aba kandi nibo bari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  39,23,"Imana yamanuye amajambo meza cane arico gitabu kirimwo amajambo ahuje n’ayandi kandi aguma asubirwamwo, urukoba rw’umubiri narwo rwama ruhinda agashitsi kuri barya batinya Umuremyi wabo, hanyuma urukoba rwabo narwo hamwe n’imitima yabo iguma ihwahutse mukwibuka Umuremyi wabo, ubwo nibwo burokoke bw’Imana, kuri ubwo burokoke irongora uwo yishakiye, kandi uwurekuriwe n’Imana yuko yazimiye, ntankundi rero uwo muntu ntawuzo murongora"
  39,24,"Mbega uwuzoba akingiye amaso yiwe n’ibihano bibi vyo k’umusi w’imperuka nayo abahemukiye imitima yabo bazobwirwa bati:- nimuhonje kuvyo mwamuye"
  39,25,"Abamyeho imbere yabo barahakanye, n’ibihano vyaraba shikiye bivuye ahantu batazi"
  39,26,Imana yaciye ibahonjesha ibimaramare mubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi n’ibihano vyo k’umusi w’imperuka nivyo bininiya iyo bobimenya
  39,27,Ntankeka abantu twaraberetse uburorero butagira uko bungana buri muri iki gitabu gitagatifu ca Qur’aani kugira ngo abantu bagume bibuka
  39,28,Iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu yamanutse mururimi rw’icarabu itarimwo ibintu bihuvya kugira ngo bikingire
  39,29,"Imana ibatangirako uburorero bw’umuntu afise basebuja bari mumatati, n’uwundi muntu afise Sebuja wiwe umwe wenyene gusa, mbega ubona yuko bongana mubuzima bwabo n’ugushimira Imana, mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bazi"
  39,30,"Mu vy’ukuri wewe uzosandaba, nabo nyene bazosandaba"
  39,31,Hanyuma ntankeka muzo kwitwara k’umusi w’imperuka imbere y’Umuremyi wanyu